{"tid":2270303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國民眾收大量神秘電話籲留在家中","createTime":"2020-11-04T03:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T03:43:37.000Z","uid":44209,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da338be1a4913dcdb6d9c681d0f152012d5f1e2f","tid":2270303,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:30:38.000Z","msg":"美國民眾收大量神秘電話籲留在家中 <br />\n2020/11/04 10:45<br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】美國大選投票期間，大量神秘電話呼籲民眾留在家中。聯邦調查局和紐約聯邦檢察官接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n在大選日，佛羅里達、艾奧瓦州等多地民眾都收到一種語音自動電話，由合成女聲，聲稱是一通測試電話，告訴人是時候留在家，保持安全，留在家中。<br />\n<br />\n雖然沒直接提及選舉，但懷疑試圖影響選民投票意慾。專家估計約一千萬選民收到電話，數據顯示今年夏季已出現這則電話，至近日特別多，業界相信源頭在外國。<br />\n<br />\n而在關鍵搖擺州密歇根，就有神秘電話散播錯誤選舉資訊，聲稱民眾為免擠擁，可在周三才親身投票，聯邦調查局亦正調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/39192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F39192&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyhURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=fc4976d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F39192&h=277a813c\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/39192</a>"},{"pid":"6c89397643ed461199d8cca44ad91fd1bd291c7c","tid":2270303,"uid":14918,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"玩假電話最叻應該係某國"},{"pid":"58b5c8b8591e78c9cc39a884a7e6c9fbac45ed8f","tid":2270303,"uid":44209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6c89397643ed461199d8cca44ad91fd1bd291c7c","tid":2270303,"uid":14918,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"玩假電話最叻應該係某國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:32:00.000Z","msg":"係中國，可以直接響名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c95b6af75556e181914b852d2d43ea1466315f","tid":2270303,"uid":258948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"58b5c8b8591e78c9cc39a884a7e6c9fbac45ed8f","tid":2270303,"uid":44209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"q